       

           RELEASE HISTORY OF THE "binda" PACKAGE


Version 1.0.2:

- Faster computation of ranking score.
- Faster is.binaryMatrix() function.
- Fix "S3 generic/method consistency" NOTE raised by R-devel.
- Updated documentation to include reference to Gibb and Strimmer (2015).


Version 1.0.1:

- Change of maintainer email address.


Version 1.0.0:

- First public release (14 April 2014)

  The "binda" package implements functions for multi-class discriminant
  analysis using binary predictors, for corresponding variable selection, 
  and for dichotomizing continuous data.
